data.description: Welcome to slice of peace and quiet. This 2.1 acreage surrounded a private conservation area is the perfect place to get away from it all.  Imagine being able to enjoy all the natural beauty of old Florida, with the benefit of this home.    This beautiful manufactured is only 5 years old sits on 2.150 acres on the corner of Country Rd 13 and Palmo Fish Camp Rd.  Only blocks from St. Johns river, to launch a boat or fishing at Palmo Boat Ramp. 3 Bed, 2 Bath, inside laundry room, master bathroom with a large tub. Vinyl plank flooring. Bring all the toys, tons of space here for that. Call for a private tour .
